<paragraph blockId="2.[259,684,286,371]" box="[356,587,350,371]" pageId="2" pageNumber="74">
<figureCitation box="[356,475,350,371]" captionStart="Figures 1–2" captionStartId="2.[164,254,1736,1755]" captionTargetBox="[174,772,1463,1706]" captionTargetId="figure-546@2.[168,776,1461,1707]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="Figures 1–2. Quichuana right antennae, lateral inner view: 1, Quichuana amazonica sp. nov., male holotype; 2, Quichuana longicauda sp. nov., female paratype; l, distance from top of basoflagellomere and most prominent point of pedicel; w, width of basoflagellomere at the level of the arista base. Scale bar: 1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5408535" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5408535/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="74">FIGURES 1</figureCitation>
